---
import PageShell from "../components/PageShell.astro";

const disclaimerBreadcrumbs = [
  { name: "Home", path: "/" },
  { name: "Disclaimer", path: "/disclaimer/" },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Important legal disclaimers regarding the use of Al Tareen."
  keywords="product manager toolkit, product management frameworks, PM frameworks, product strategy, prioritization, Altareen"
breadcrumbs={disclaimerBreadcrumbs}
>
  <section class="legalPage" aria-label="Disclaimer">
    <div class="legalContainer">
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="effective">Effective Date: March 25, 2026</p>

      <p>
        The information provided on <strong>Al Tareen</strong> (https://altareen.com)
        is for informational and educational purposes only. By accessing or using
        this website, you acknowledge and agree to the terms outlined below.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Informational Purposes Only</h2>
      <p>
        All content, including frameworks, tools, concepts, and materials, is
        provided for general informational purposes only and does not constitute
        financial, legal, tax, investment, or professional advice.
      </p>
      <p>
        You should not rely on any content on this website as a substitute for
        professional consultation. Always seek advice from qualified professionals
        before making decisions.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Independent Judgment</h2>
      <p>
        All decisions made based on the content of this website are your sole
        responsibility. You are expected to apply independent judgment, validation,
        and due diligence before acting on any information.
      </p>

      <h2>3. No Guarantees</h2>
      <p>
        No guarantees are made regarding outcomes, performance, or results derived
        from the use of any frameworks, models, or concepts presented.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outcomes depend on execution, context, external conditions, and individual
        capability.
      </p>

      <h2>4. User Contributions (Feedback System)</h2>
      <p>
        This website may allow users to submit feedback (such as likes or dislikes)
        on frameworks. These interactions are aggregated for informational purposes only.
      </p>
      <p>
        User feedback does not represent verified data, professional evaluation,
        or endorsed conclusions.
      </p>

      <h2>5. External Links</h2>
      <p>
        This website may contain links to third-party websites or tools. These are
        provided for convenience only.
      </p>
      <p>
        Al Tareen does not control or assume responsibility for the content,
        policies, or practices of third-party services.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        All original content, including proprietary frameworks, structure, and
        materials, is the intellectual property of Al Tareen unless otherwise stated.
      </p>
      <p>
        Unauthorized reproduction, distribution, or misuse is prohibited.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, Al Tareen disclaims all liability
        for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising
        from the use of this website.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Changes</h2>
      <p>
        This Disclaimer may be updated at any time without prior notice.
        Continued use of the website constitutes acceptance of any updates.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For inquiries:
        <a href="mailto:altareenk@outlook.com">altareenk@outlook.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>


<style is:global>
  html, body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .legalPage {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 0 64px;
    display: flow-root;
  }

  .legalContainer {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--border) 74%, transparent);
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 98%, white 2%),
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 98%, black 2%)
      );
    box-shadow:
      0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.62) inset,
      0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.018);
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .effective {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  p {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 12px 18px;
    padding: 0;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
  }

  a:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  /* Fix header logo unwanted styling */
  header a,
  .logo {
    border: none !important;
    background: transparent !important;
    box-shadow: none !important;
  }

  /* Remove underline from footer links */
  footer a {
    text-decoration: none !important;
    border-bottom: none !important;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .legalContainer {
      padding: 16px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
</PageShell>